sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant MainWorker as Primary Worker
    participant Heartbeat as Heartbeat Thread
    participant Redis as Redis Storage
    participant PeerWorker as Peer Recovery Worker

    MainWorker->>MainWorker: Read message (msg_id) via XREADGROUP
    MainWorker->>Heartbeat: Add msg_id to self.active_jobs
    
    loop Every 30 seconds
        Heartbeat->>Redis: SET job_lease:{msg_id} "1" EX 120
    end

    Note over MainWorker: Worker Process Crashes (SIGKILL)
    Note over Heartbeat: Heartbeat Loop Terminates
    Note over Redis: Key job_lease:{msg_id} Expires after 120s

    Note over PeerWorker: 5 minutes later (min_idle_time = 300000ms)
    PeerWorker->>Redis: XAUTOCLAIM min_idle=300000 count=10
    Redis-->>PeerWorker: Return [msg_id, payload]
    PeerWorker->>Redis: EXISTS job_lease:{msg_id}
    Redis-->>PeerWorker: 0 (Lease Expired)
    PeerWorker->>PeerWorker: Re-execute & resume from last step
